name: Catz #1
description: Introducing 'Catz' - a collection of randomly generated NFT cats! Each 'Catz' is a unique digital collectible, featuring adorable and quirky cat characters. Whether you're collecting for fun or investment, there's a Catz waiting to brighten your digital world!
